metadata.name: 8lements
metadata.description: 8lements is an 8k animated art collection NFT landscape which evolves around eight different type of elements. The elements consists of Fire, Ice, Wind, Water, Earth, Light, Darkness, and Lightning. In essence, the core foundations of 8LEMENTS revolves around environmental awareness and to shine a bright light on this matter through our 8 elements ideology. Additionally, this concept combined with the brilliant art work of our talented artist, Bigmouth Studio, will not only allow for a successful NFT journey, but to convey a much greater message for the good of our environment.
